data.description: TRUE PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP! This 3BD/1BTH one-of-a-kind Cape has been remodeled from top to bottom, inside and out, and features 3 levels of living space with a detached 2 car garage and sits on 0.14 landscaped acres with panoramic city & mountain views in the heart of Scranton! The perfect marriage of classic craftsman architecture with modern flair! Sunny, bright with new lighting, hardware and fresh paint throughout! The Kitchen/Dining area is well appointed, has soft-close cabinets with glass inserts, ample counter space, stainless appliances and a sun room! The Primary Bedroom features wood floors, a reading nook & a custom dressing area with attic storage. The Basement is fully finished, modern and features a built-in gas fireplace in the Family Room and has extra space for a home office, gym, craft or play area. Custom Laundry Room & bonus storage area too! Relax on the covered front porch or retreat to the back patio & enjoy the fully fenced & landscaped yard & views! SEE OUR LIST OF UPDATES & RENOVATIONS! A MUST SEE!
